49
00:04:58,131 --> 00:04:59,132
Kau sudah tahu sejak awal?

50
00:04:59,508 --> 00:05:01,468
Terluka akibat pisau,
tangan terbakar...

51
00:05:01,676 --> 00:05:03,094
Ukirlah pelajaran-pelajaran itu di tubuhmu.

52
00:05:03,178 --> 00:05:05,096
