Hei! Bisakah kita minta nasi lagi?

206
00:15:43,443 --> 00:15:44,444
Beras!

207
00:15:44,527 --> 00:15:46,779
- Nasi, nasi, nasi, nasi.
- Nasi, nasi, nasi, nasi.

